---
// Footer moderno, con contraste y espaciamiento
---
<footer class="footer-modern">
  <div class="footer-content">
    &copy; 2025 <span class="footer-brand">Hotel Gneis</span>. Todos los derechos reservados.
  </div>
</footer>
<style>
.footer-modern {
  width: 100%;
  background: var(--color-dark);
  border-top: 1.5px solid #222c2c;
  padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem 0;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 -2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
}

.footer-content {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  color: #f6f8f8;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1px;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

.footer-brand {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .footer-modern {
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 0 1rem 0;
  }
}
</style>
